UID:CksaK02-QPRoBwTFfkRib
SUMMARY:Immigration Justice Working Group Migrant Accompaniment Training
DTSTAMP:20260326T011012Z
DTSTART:20260328T100000Z
DESCRIPTION:ICE is kidnapping our neighbors off the streets and at their im
	migration and legal appointments. Join us to be trained in accompanying mi
	grants to their appointments\\\, to help protect their legal rights\\\, an
	d connect them to critical resources. \\nAll volunteers providing accompan
	iment must be willing to opt into a state background check.\n\nhttps://sea
	ttledsa.org/event/immigration-justice-working-group-migrant-accompaniment-
	training-2/\n\nFrom Seattle DSA
URL:https://seattledsa.org/event/immigration-justice-working-group-migrant-
