BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:1RK1nOtsJ3R9hAHaCYLVI
SUMMARY:Ecosocialism and Green New Deal Working Group
DTSTAMP:20260326T011012Z
DTSTART:20260330T200000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us biweekly for continued conversations about our vision a
	nd strategies for ecosocialist politics. Ecosocialism promotes democratic 
	control over all institutions that impact life and the environment. A Gree
	n New Deal (GND) distills actions to address the climate crisis through a 
	rapid and just transformation of these institutions. Questions? Please con
