UID:gkSwxAEDW6L7FiVRc_zH7
SUMMARY:Socialist Educators Happy Hour
DTSTAMP:20260326T011013Z
DTSTART:20260410T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Socialist Educators Happy Hour\\nEducators from all over (Seatt
	le\\\, Renton\\\, Highline\\\, etc…) get together\\\, chat politics\\\, & 
	share about struggles in their union. All union activists and socialists a
	re welcome to attend! \\nWe often anchor our discussions with a reading\\\
